# ============================================
# 🔴 CRITICAL: External Supabase Database Configuration
# ============================================
# This application MUST use the external Supabase database.
# DO NOT use local databases or other Supabase projects.
#
# External Supabase URL: https://maqzxlcsgfpwnfyleoga.supabase.co
# Project Ref: maqzxlcsgfpwnfyleoga
#
# Contact the team for the actual credentials.
